<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="battle-n">battle <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'bætl/    美 /'bætl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 战役；战斗；斗争；较量：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>fight a battle 
打仗；作战</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a long-running <strong>legal battle</strong>
一场旷日持久的法律争讼</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A good beginning is half the battle. 
良好的开始是成功的一半。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I realized running was a <strong>battle against</strong> myself.
我意识到跑步是一场与自己的较量。</p><footer>2018 北京</footer></div></div>